	   <tr><td colspan=2> Hi, This is my first time posting but I have a proplem about people taking advantage of newbies with enchanted items, And now with new focus items it's worse. I once was almost in big truble because of theese focus items, Lukly I didn't pay for them if I had I would have been In HUGE trouble! you see the night after the new patch I found some packages on the ground and dicided to investigate. I picked them up and found that they were braclets and rings. Being better than my current ones I equiped them. I almost sold my previous braclets when I became link dead. When I was back on the right before I clicked the trade button I realised the rings and bracelets dissapeard. I was almost a victim of loosing soe good equip, and now newbies have been. So if your a person that can enchant theese items then make sure that you clearly state the'll disapeer after loging. Don't let newbies be the victim because you used to be just like them belive it or not.<br>&nbsp;<br>Lord Celris TreeWalker Enchanter of the World</td></tr>
