	   <tr><td colspan=2>Excellent storytelling, as usual.&nbsp;&nbsp;You've an excellent gift, and I would say once again you should write a novel with Shrikke as the main character.  I would definitely be one of the owners of such a book, and I'm sure many others here agree.<br>&nbsp;<br>Icewind Novastorm<br>Koada Dal Cleric of Tunare<br>&lt;&lt;Mith Marr&gt;&gt;</td></tr>
