	   <tr><td colspan=2>Shrikke's adventures as a broodling are outstanding!&nbsp;&nbsp;I don't play dark races, it just doesn't work for me.  So, when I started to read this journal, I was skeptical.  But the more I read it, the more fascinating it became.  <br><br>I've read that the evil races of Norrath don't consider themselves evil.  This journal sheds a lot of light on that, and one can begin to understand the mind of the Iksar.<br><br>If no more is written about Shrikke, that would be unfortunate.  If Parttime did no more writing, THAT would be a tragedy.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Arjaizen Izrhume<br>31st Circle Wizard of Erudin<br>Fallen Wolves</td></tr>
