	   <tr><td colspan=2>It is well that you curry my favor!&nbsp;&nbsp;The alternative if you sought to displease me is a visit with the "Cuddler", my Torturer-in-Chief (a most unpleasent meeting, I assure you).<br><br>I find you, along with Tochail, Mugali, and others to be of scientific interest to me.  I wish to study the habits and movements of lower lifeforms and thereby predict their behavior.  By mapping out your responses to my needlings I shall determine a course of action in regards to my Great Offensive (tm), which should take place in the near future, Innoruuk willing!  This will  be valuable information for my minions when they come into contact with your kind so that unexpected action does not occur-- rather, when faced with the terrifying prospect of having a Jaded Mace come crashing down on your skull and running off beforehand making it twice the effort for my armies, you will stand stock-still in utter fear of my invading hordes.<br><br>You see, by desensitising you to the awesome and horror-instilling presence of Evil, you will become innured to it, thus standing still, waiting placidly for your death.<br><br>Cunning, isn't it?  And this is only the beginning...<br>...hrrrrrr hrrrrr hrrrrr!<br><br>--Pusbag Infection<br>&nbsp;<br>Emperor and Shamanic High Priest of the Trolls<br>"Worship Innoruuk, you worthless cattle!"<br></td></tr>
