	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ah, Shrikke, it seems that your stories have taken on the edge of the conflict we have within Cabilis.&nbsp;&nbsp;Though you killed a fellow necromancer, he was male, and obviously weak, so of no consequence.  Know though, that the Brood of Kotiz, and my own Wurmbane Brood are watching your writings very carefully...  be careful where you go... lest the serpent strike you down.<br><br>Usula of the Wurmbane<br>Queen of Fear<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
